===Noun===
'''[[grammar]] [[school]]'''

# {{archaic}} A school that teaches its pupils the grammar system of a European language, especially [[Latin]] and [[Greek]].
# {{cattag|mostly British}} A [[secondary]] school that stresses [[academic]] over [[practical]] or [[vocational]] [[education]], until recent times open to those [[pupil]]s who had passed the [[11-plus examination]].
# {{US}} [[elementary school|Elementary school]].

